<h1>Next Bus Countdown</h1>

An applet that counts down to the next buses leaving from the NRC
<H2>Important notes</H2>
<UL>
<LI>The bus times are at the <B>closest stop</B> listed in the table
so 61 and 185 might be a bit early, 84 might be a little late.
<LI>This uses weekday times, so on the weekend, look it up yourself or, better, go have fun instead of working.
<LI>Feel free to download the code, but note that its ludicrously sloppy.  
</UL>

<applet code="NextBus.class" width="400" height="400" clockFontSize="36">

Your browser is completely ignoring the &lt;APPLET&gt; tag!

</applet>
<BR>
It now runs on my Nokia - you can get
<A HREF="http://tiredrobot.blogspot.com/2010/03/writing-mobile-phone-app.html"> more details on the blog</A>.

